{
  "stem": "8947.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Although, I didn't speak a single word of Hungarian-- Romanian, because we were speaking Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- So what happened then, in 19-- the Hungarians resented the loss of Transylvania.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a bait for them from Hitler to tell them, like you put the little cheese to the mouse.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If you join me and you agree with my policies you are going to get back Transylvania.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Hungarians joined Hitler, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, suddenly, the government was toward Nazis and fascist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, naturally, this affected us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And why did they join?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a political and economic difficulty, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so they joined them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then anti-Jewish laws came gradually in function.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told you my father, they attacked already the people who were in important positions.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then only a limited number of Jewish students were accepted the gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you had an-- an exam at the end of the fourth elementary school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you didn't score high, if you were a Jew, you never could get your education.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When you were in a school, they were accepted seven students for a classroom.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this is when I really experienced for the first time real Jewish persecution, not only discrimination.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because in school, for instance, we were asked every single day, the Jewish students, who are the Jewish students, so that we can be prosecuted.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If didn't know-- if, for instance, the Romanians didn't know a question-- the teacher ask the Jew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If the Jew didn't know, the Jew got a bad grade.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You got the bad grade, you were flunking out of school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then when you came out, you know, you had limericks, degrading limericks verses and stones thrown after you.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
